To play the game, run:

ruby Game.rb 


The game must be played with 2 players (there is no AI). 
In order to move a piece, you must provide a row, column, and direction. 

Valid directions: 
north
north-east
east
south-east
south
south-west
west
north-west

example move command: 

move 0 5 south 
  //will move the piece in the top-most row, 5th column, downwards 


